[DEBUG] Start reload packge "Automatos::Wrapper::Tool::Vplex"
Reload Packge "Automatos::Wrapper::Tool::Vplex" done


Load Test Module
================
Load Test Module quickly, so that all APIs of Test Case module can be easily called by $self->API()

./automatos-shell.pl -t vplex.xml -p SSIETests::VNX2::Interoperability::Vplex::Base


